{"tid":1812774,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鎮暴警察制服上出現細藍線（thin blue line）","createTime":"2020-01-05T17:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T04:21:33.000Z","uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ca29359bad87f347cc530ddff4cbcc8402539690","tid":1812774,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTUCrRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTUCrRQ.jpg&h=2dd83f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ojKRje.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ojKRje.jpg&h=f4825de3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ginkgoesd328/status/1213784219157008384?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fginkgoesd328%2Fstatus%2F1213784219157008384%3Fs%3D19&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1aDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=7030aadd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fginkgoesd328%2Fstatus%2F1213784219157008384%3Fs%3D19&h=8692f39e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ginkgoesd328/status/1213784219157008384?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n習語thin blue line在美國很常見，香港卻很少用到。它有幾個意思，其中一個意思是警隊代表了保護社會免陷入無法紀、混亂（chaos）與罪惡之中的那道細小的防線。它被稱為藍線，因為藍色是警隊制服的傳統顏色。另一個意思是細藍線（thin blue line）代表了生死間的一線之差，因為警察每天都要面對很多的危險。在美國，黑色背景配上一條細藍線（thin blue line）的圖案亦很常見，有些人會將圖案置於車身上，以表達對警隊的支持。在黑底上加一條細藍線（thin blue line）也可以是悼念警察執勤時殉職。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/columns/126/20190627/775525/%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E5%8F%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%88%E8%8B%B1-thin-blue-line\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fcolumns%2F126%2F20190627%2F775525%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E5%258F%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258F%2588%25E8%258B%25B1-thin-blue-line&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1aDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=1d90790a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fcolumns%2F126%2F20190627%2F775525%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E5%258F%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258F%2588%25E8%258B%25B1-thin-blue-line&h=3969963a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/columns/126/20190627/775525/%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E5%8F%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%88%E8%8B%B1-thin-blue-line</a><br />\n<br />\n牠們以為自己好似美國警察咁危險，扮辛苦扮慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12a313dbe373f73c39fd16c56a4b7e8f59ea939","tid":1812774,"uid":283587,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"其實係咪藍絲咁解"},{"pid":"a4c21975a3bf674580eeada050f31554f4c04053","tid":1812774,"uid":128102,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T17:55:51.000Z","msg":"無位擺證又有一大堆垃圾<br />\n不知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f31b23661ca9d8d51831a0bc587359f1b772f1","tid":1812774,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c12a313dbe373f73c39fd16c56a4b7e8f59ea939","tid":1812774,"uid":283587,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"其實係咪藍絲咁解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T17:56:07.000Z","msg":"The &quot;Thin Blue Line&quot; is a phrase that refers figuratively to the position of police in society as the force which holds back chaos, allowing order and civilization to thrive.<br />\n<br />\n即係話自己好似前排軍人，為社會搵命搏<br />\n實際上香港警察只為中共港共效力，回覆所謂的「秩序」"},{"pid":"12d9680a0b08ce1fecb26c99bbea656062146841","tid":1812774,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T17:56:29.000Z","msg":"知唔知醜"},{"pid":"8927c6ad13b30d14c9cc898ae67452d591a760ca","tid":1812774,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:02:29.000Z","msg":"圍威喂打飛機"},{"pid":"fe7148f4689fa6cf8cd3f484d966339901627e89","tid":1812774,"uid":127929,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"rep